---
---

<section class="the-ask" id="ask">
  <div class="ask-content">
    <h2 class="ask-heading">What We're Asking For</h2>

    <div class="asks-grid">
      <div class="ask-item">
        <span class="ask-number">1</span>
        <div class="ask-text">
          <h3 class="ask-title">Co-funding commitments</h3>
          <p class="ask-description">
            Even soft or conditional commitments give us a credible signal of
            demand when approaching sponsors.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ask-item">
        <span class="ask-number">2</span>
        <div class="ask-text">
          <h3 class="ask-title">Permission to name the Alliance in sponsor outreach</h3>
          <p class="ask-description">
            Any formal partnership agreements will come back to you for review
            before signing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ask-item">
        <span class="ask-number">3</span>
        <div class="ask-text">
          <h3 class="ask-title">Feedback and topic requests</h3>
          <p class="ask-description">
            What questions are most pressing for your members? What domains are
            most represented in your network? Early input shapes the curriculum
            most.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .the-ask {
    position: relative;
    background-color: var(--color-orange);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl);
    padding-inline: var(--space-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .the-ask::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(
      ellipse at 30% 20%,
      rgba(245, 135, 44, 0.4) 0%,
      transparent 50%
    ),
    radial-gradient(
      ellipse at 70% 80%,
      rgba(196, 64, 26, 0.3) 0%,
      transparent 40%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .ask-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .ask-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .asks-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .ask-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.15);
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(237, 221, 200, 0.1);
    transition: all var(--transition-medium);
  }

  .ask-item:hover {
    background-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.25);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .ask-number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    background-color: var(--color-cream);
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.2);
  }

  .ask-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .ask-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ask-description {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    opacity: 0.9;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .asks-grid {
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .ask-item {
      padding: var(--space-xl);
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .ask-number {
      width: 3rem;
      height: 3rem;
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
    }

    .ask-title {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
    }

    .ask-description {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .the-ask {
      padding-block: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .ask-heading {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .ask-item {
      padding: var(--space-md);
    }

    .ask-number {
      width: 2rem;
      height: 2rem;
      font-size: var(--text-base);
    }

    .ask-title {
      font-size: var(--text-base);
    }

    .ask-description {
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .ask-item {
      transition: none;
    }

    .ask-item:hover {
      transform: none;
    }
  }
</style>
